title: Gary Willis - Progressive Bassics
description:
Gary Willis: Progressive bassics

Former bassist of Tribal Tech. Willis has a really unique right hand picking technique which really worth learning. However if you've played the bass for a long time it'll be really hard. I recommend this lesson to absolute beginners. The quality is not the best because this is a VHS rip. But I don't think it's important because the video's content is completely understandable and (in my opinion) really useful. Also, forgive me that I cannot include the booklet of the lesson in this torrent; I'm only glad that I could get the video! It wasn't easy. Whatever, have fun and play music!
